{"product_id":"young-rich-mighty-ii","title":"YOUNG RICH MIGHTY II","description":"\u003cp\u003e260 GSM. Premium Heavyweight Fabric. High-Detail Puff Print Front \u0026amp; Back. Gender-Neutral. Relaxed Fit. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed. Exclusive YRM Limited Edition.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis 260 GSM premium T-shirt from the exclusive YRM limited-edition collection is designed to make a bold, unmistakable statement. Crafted from heavyweight fabric, it offers a structured yet breathable feel that delivers all-day comfort with a strong streetwear presence. The front and back feature intricately detailed \u003cstrong\u003e“YOUNG RICH MIGHTY”\u003c\/strong\u003e artwork executed in high-definition puff print, creating a striking raised texture that adds depth, dimension, and a premium visual impact. Designed for those who stand out effortlessly, this piece blends luxury aesthetics with everyday wearability. Combed and bio-washed for superior softness and long-lasting durability, it maintains its shape and finish over time while elevating your wardrobe with a powerful identity.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to preserve fabric quality and puff print detailing. Do not iron directly on the prints. Store in a cool, dry place.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e260 GSM premium heavyweight fabric for a structured, high-end feel. Relaxed, gender-neutral fit designed for statement streetwear. High-detail “YOUNG RICH MIGHTY” puff print on both front and back for elevated texture and depth. Exclusive YRM limited-edition release for a distinctive look. Combed and bio-washed fabric for enhanced softness, durability, and long-term shape retention.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47682205384858,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47682205417626,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47682205450394,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47682205483162,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XXL","offer_id":47682205515930,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"XS","offer_id":47687032373402,"sku":"oversizedtees-1","price":2199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00325_copy.webp?v=1774686690","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/young-rich-mighty-ii","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}